Tools for testing and running init executables.
piu-pack must be run as superuser
and piu-copy takes in an argument (the init executable)

creates test user
username: test
password: password

Order:
./piu-gendir
./piu-copy (init file)
./piu-pack
./piu-qemu
./piu-clean

THIS IS UNTESTED ON 99% OF SYSTEMS AND USES DANGEROUS COMMANDS (mkfs, losetup, etc...) USE AT YOUR OWN RISK.
